body:
@sammoes did you figure this out?

EDIT:
This did the trick for me. Modify `LINK_OPTS` in `bazel-tensorflow/external/protobuf/BUILD` by adding the `-lm` flag to `//conditions:default`:

```
LINK_OPTS = select({
    ":android": [],
    "//conditions:default": ["-lpthread", "-lm"],
})
```
